entries.title_d: Exchange cargo with the CorSec Lancer, then take the decoy to another CorSec craft.
entries.title: Dathomir System: Courier a Decoy Between Two CorSec Fighters
entries.split_quest_alert: \#pcontrast3 CorSec Command: < \#pcontrast1 A Black Sun attack group is heading your way, be ready. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.quest_rendezvous2_d: Travel here leading enemy attention away from the Lancer
entries.quest_rendezvous1_d: Travel here to offload the Weapons Shipment you captured earlier
entries.quest_location_d: An area of heavy Black Sun activity in the Dathomir System
entries.quest_dock2_d: Deliver the fake cargo to this ship.
entries.quest_dock1_d: Make a switch for some fake weapons grade materials with this craft for your Weapons Shipment
entries.hello_p: \#pcontrast3 Transmission: < \#pcontrast1 Lets get a move on, this transfer needs to be quick.  I have a surprise for you. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.hello_d: \#pcontrast3 Transmission: < \#pcontrast1 Hurry up on the dock, this area is hot. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.found_loc_p: \#pcontrast3 Nav Computer: < \#pcontrast1 Contact point for our delivery ship has been received. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.found_loc_d: \#pcontrast3 Nav Computer: < \#pcontrast1 Contact point for the decoy ship has been received. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.failed_destroyed: You have failed because a delivery craft was destroyed.
entries.docking_complete_pickup: \#pcontrast3 Transmission: < \#pcontrast1 We are transfering the weapons from you now.  Take this warhead to an Interceptor a few clicks over, it has a large sensor output and will help throw Black Sun persuit off my tail \#pcontrast3 >
entries.docking_complete_delivery: \#pcontrast3 Transmission: < \#pcontrast1 The docking is complete, transfer your cargo and move out, Command reports more ships heading this way. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.attack_stopped: \#pcontrast3 Tactical Computer: < \#pcontrast1 The attack has been stopped. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.attack_notify: \#pcontrast3 Tactical Computer: < \#pcontrast1 Enemy craft detected on attack vector. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.arrived_at_pickup: \#pcontrast3 Nav Computer: < \#pcontrast1 Designated pickup point reached. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.arrived_at_delivery: \#pcontrast3 Nav Computer: < \#pcontrast1 Designated delivery point reached. \#pcontrast3 >
